Interface DrawableEntity

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Critter, Critter_Cyan, Critter_Orange, Critter_Pink, Critter_Red, Critter_White, Critter_Yellow, TDMap, Tower, Tower_Fire, Tower_IceBeam, Tower_Laser, Tower_SpreadShot

    public interface DrawableEntity
    This is an interface from which all game entities much implement. This is so that all entities have an updateAndDraw() method, for chronology.

    v1.0.0
    Author:
    HaoZhang
